README for Siesta 0.5

=head1 NAME

Siesta - the main class for the Siesta mailing list manager.


=head1 DEPENDENCIES

This module has external dependencies on the following modules:

 Apache::Session::SharedMem
 Class::Accessor::Fast
 Class::DBI::BaseDSN
 Class::DBI::SQLite
 Digest::MD5
 Email::LocalDelivery	0.02
 Email::Simple	1.4
 File::Basename
 File::Find::Rule
 File::Path
 Mail::Address
 Mail::DeliveryStatus::BounceParser
 Module::Build	0.18
 Storable
 String::ShellQuote
 Template
 Test::More
 Tie::IxHash
 UNIVERSAL::require

=head1 INSTALLATION

 perl Build.PL
 perl Build test

and if all goes well

 perl Build install

